=Analyze the following Tax4Us content request and generate comprehensive writing guidelines:

Title: {{ $json.title }}
Keywords: {{ $json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Topic: {{ $json.topic }}
Target Audience: {{ $json.targetAudience }}
Content Type: {{ $json.contentType }}
Word Count: {{ $json.wordCount }}

Generate JSON output with:
- search_intent (informational/transactional/navigational/commercial)
- writing_style (professional and authoritative for tax/accounting)
- writing_tone (trustworthy and helpful for tax clients)
- target_audience (small business owners, individuals, tax professionals)
- goal_of_article (educate on tax topics, provide guidance, build trust)
- semantic_analysis (common tax subtopics and related questions)
- keywords (primary, secondary, semantic, long-tail)

Focus on Tax4Us brand voice: professional, trustworthy, helpful for tax and accounting needs in Israel.

=Create an SEO-optimized title for Tax4Us content:

Working Title: {{ $json.title }}
Keywords: {{ $('Process Request').first().json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Search Intent: {{ $json.search_intent }}
Writing Style: {{ $json.writing_style }}

Generate a title that:
- Is professional and trustworthy (Tax4Us brand)
- Includes the primary keyword naturally
- Appeals to tax clients and small business owners in Israel
- Is 50-60 characters for SEO
- Uses power words when appropriate

Output only the refined title as JSON: {"refined_title": "Your Title Here"}

