Generate a detailed outline with:
- Main sections (H2 headings)
- Subsections (H3 headings)
- Key points for each section
- SEO considerations
- Israeli tax context integration
- Professional tone throughout

Format as structured markdown with clear hierarchy.

=Write the main content body for Tax4Us article:

Title: {{ $json.refined_title }}
Introduction: {{ $json.introduction }}
Outline: {{ $json.content_outline }}
Key Takeaways: {{ $json.key_takeaways }}
Keywords: {{ $('Process Request').first().json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Target Word Count: {{ $('Process Request').first().json.wordCount }}

Create comprehensive content that:
- Follows the outline structure
- Integrates keywords naturally
- Provides valuable tax insights for Israeli businesses
- Uses professional but accessible language
- Includes practical examples and tips
- Builds trust in Tax4Us expertise
- Addresses Israeli tax regulations and compliance

Write in markdown format with proper headings and formatting.

=Combine all content sections into a complete Tax4Us article:

Title: {{ $json.refined_title }}
Introduction: {{ $json.introduction }}
Content Body: {{ $json.content_body }}
Conclusion: {{ $json.conclusion }}
Key Takeaways: {{ $json.key_takeaways }}

Create a complete, polished article that:
- Flows smoothly from introduction to conclusion
- Maintains consistent professional tone
- Integrates all sections seamlessly
- Optimizes for SEO and readability
- Includes proper formatting and structure
- Focuses on Israeli tax context
- Builds trust in Tax4Us expertise

Format as complete markdown with proper headings, paragraphs, and structure.

